<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7664865>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Chaetopleura pustulata (Krauss, 1848): (A–D) partly disarticulated syntype of Chiton pustulatus Krauss, 1848 (SMNH # 4983): (A) dorsal view of the syntype, showing valves ii, iii and vii in situ, anterior at right, (B) dorsal view of valve iv, anterior at top, (C) dorsal view of the tail valve, anterior at top, (D) ventral view of the tail valve, anterior at top; (E–F) isolated valves of the holotype of Chaetopleura natalensis Kaas & Van Belle, 1990 (NM D4842): (E) dorsal view of the tail valve, anterior at top, (F) dorsal view of the right half of valve iv, anterior at top. Scale bars A = 2 mm, B–F = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7664865/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

